==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reseizer
<hw>Re*seiz"er</hw> <pr>(-s?z"?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who seizes again.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Eng. Law)</fld> <def>The taking of lands into the
hands of the king where a general livery, or <xex>oustre le main</xex>,
was formerly mis-sued, contrary to the form and order of law.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reseizure</ent>⟦br⟧
